Name: Starlight  Diamond Lv.3
Description: Through Gemcrafting, raw ore can be processed into a higher-level diamond.
Description$english: Through Gemcrafting, raw ore can be processed into a higher-level diamond.
Description2$english: A rare raw stone grown in Regnus, bringing an indescribable sense of opportunity. Like encountering a clear spring in the deep mountains when thirsty. or like picking up a seashell on the beach just before the tide rises. Or perhaps a fragment of a star falling into your palm through the gap between inevitability and chance.
